.TH "dwc2_hc_start_transfer_ddma" 9 "dwc2_hc_start_transfer_ddma" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
dwc2_hc_start_transfer_ddma \- Does the setup for a data transfer for a host channel and starts the transfer in Descriptor DMA mode
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "void" dwc2_hc_start_transfer_ddma
.BI "(struct dwc2_hsotg *hsotg "  ","
.BI "struct dwc2_host_chan *chan "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "hsotg" 12
Programming view of DWC_otg controller
.IP "chan" 12
Information needed to initialize the host channel
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Initializes HCTSIZ register. For a PING transfer the Do Ping bit is set.
Sets PID and NTD values. For periodic transfers initializes SCHED_INFO field
with micro-frame bitmap.

Initializes HCDMA register with descriptor list address and CTD value then
starts the transfer via enabling the channel.
